    <h2 id="keywords">Keywords</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://ads.google.com/home/tools/keyword-planner/">Google Keyword Planner</a> [<a href="https://backlinko.com/google-keyword-planner">Article</a>]</li>
      <li><a href="https://authoritywebsiteincome.com/best-kw-research-tool-keyword-competitiveness/">KWFinder</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://keywordtool.io/amazon">Amazon‚Äôs Kewordtool.io</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.seocentro.com/tools/search-engines/keyword-position.html">Check your raking for a given keyword</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://answerthepublic.com/">answerthepublic.com</a> - finds questions, prepositions, comparisons, alphabeticals, and related searches.</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.google.com/trends/correlate">Google Correlate</a> - finds search patterns corresponding with real‚Äêworld trends</li>
      <li><a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/how-to-use-google-trends-for-keyword-research/">How to use Google Trends for Keyword Research</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://trends.google.com">Google Trends</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://my.jaaxy.com">Jaaxy</a> - has ‚Äúquoted search result‚Äù feature, good for determining keyword competition</li>
      <li><a href="http://keywordshitter.com">Keyword Shitter</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://seo.danzambonini.com">AdWord &amp; SEO Keyword Permutation Generator</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://www.wordstream.com/free-keyword-tools">Wordstream Free Keyword Tools</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://topvisor.com/">Topvisor</a> - keyword tools - monitors the position of web pages for different keywords on Search Engine Result Pages.</li>
      <li><a href="http://www.keywordeye.com/">Keywordeye</a> -  keyword reserach with visualizations</li>
      <li><a href="http://www.ntopic.org/">nTopic</a> - gives your content a ‚Äúrelevancy score‚Äù and offers keyword suggestions to improve it.</li>
      <li><a href="https://keywordseverywhere.com/">Keywordseverywhere.com</a> - browser addon providing search volume, CPC &amp; competitive data.</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.wordtracker.com/scout">Wordtracker Scout</a> - extension that grabs the most relevant keywords from a web-page.</li>
      <li><a href="https://soovle.com/">Soovle</a> - suggested keywords from Google, YouTube, Bing, Amazon and more.</li>
      <li><a href="https://serps.com/tools/rank_checker">SERPS - Rank Checker</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.seedkeywords.com">seedkeywords.com</a></li>
    </ul>

