    <h2 id="link-building">Link Building</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="http://www.boomeranggmail.com/">Boomerang</a> - follow-up email reminders.</li>
      <li><a href="http://tools.buzzstream.com/link-building">Buzzstream Tools Suite</a> -</li>
      <li><a href="https://netvantagemarketing.com/about/domain-hunter-plus">Domain Hunter Plus</a> - Chrome extension to check for broken links.</li>
      <li><a href="http://email-format.com/">email-format.com</a> - find the email address formats in use at thousands of companies</li>
      <li><a href="http://www.google.com/mapmaker">Google Mapmaker</a> - allows you to contribute to public map information, which may be shared and incorporated into Google Maps.</li>
      <li><a href="http://www.linkstant.com/">linkstant.com</a> - alerts you when you recieve a link</li>
      <li><a href="http://linksy.me/find-email">Linksy.me Email Guesser</a></li>
      <li><a href="http://mailtester.com/">mailtester.com</a> - check an e-mail address without sending it a spam test message</li>
      <li><a href="http://myblogguest.com/">MyBlogGuest</a> - Find Guest Posting opportunities</li>
      <li><a href="http://www.majesticseo.com/">Majestic SEO</a> - Link Research\Building, Competitive Analysis - free options great for link research.</li>
    </ul>

