    <h2 id="api">API</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="http://www.sharedcount.com/documentation.php">SharedCount API</a> - combined statistics of Google+, Twitter, Facebook, and more.</li>
      <li><a href="https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/1008004?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=1008008">Google Analytics API</a> -for building custom reports and tools, and also for pulling data straight into Excel or Google Docs.</li>
      <li><a href="http://seogadget.com/api/">SEOgadget Links API</a> - lets you gather backlink data and contact information.</li>
