    <p>You can minimize your chances of avoiding a huge impact by always focusing on the SEO fundamentals. Avoid any shortcuts or spammy tactics that may have short-term gains but could create disaster in the long term.</p>

    <p>You‚Äôre far better off understanding your audience and creating content that builds your authority, relevance, and trust.</p>

